data.description: Attention all ranch homebuyers! Adorable 3 bedroom,  1 1/2 bath ranch home with 2 car garage. Step into the generous sized living room featuring beautiful refinished hardwood floors and large coat closet. The kitchen has updated wood cabinets, appliances and enough space to include a large table area. 3 bedrooms have beautiful refinished hardwood floors and high windows for easy furniture placement. Both bath have had updates. Laundry room includes washer and dryer. Other updates include newer windows, roof and vinyl siding which compliments the stone work. Covered patio is ideal for your morning/evening beverage of choice overlooking your private yard highlighted by the screened gazebo, gas fire pit and refreshing above ground pool. Oversized two car garage. Award winning schools are Windsor grade, South middle and Prospect high. Close to parks, shopping, restaurants, train and more. Don't miss out on this special home.
